rows.label: qst202719_0010
rows.name: Mimumu...

rows.label: qst202719_0020
rows.name: Mother...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202719_0030
rows.name: Go on, go to her.

rows.label: qst202719_0040
rows.name: Mother... I'm sorry, mo.

rows.label: qst202719_0050
rows.name: I'm sorry for worrying you, mo.

rows.label: qst202719_0060
rows.name: No...[ML:Dash ] I'm just glad you're safe, mo.

rows.label: qst202719_0070
rows.name: Are you hurt anywhere, mo?

rows.label: qst202719_0080
rows.name:
No, I'm okay, mo. Mei-san and
the others protected me, mo.

rows.label: qst202719_0090
rows.name:
I see, that's good,
mo...[ML:Dash ] I'm so glad, mo.

rows.label: qst202719_0100
rows.name: Mother... Mimumu was wrong, mo.

rows.label: qst202719_0110
rows.name:
I blamed everything on everyone
else and just ran away...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202719_0120
rows.name:
I should have talked to
you more, Mother...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202719_0130
rows.name: It's not your fault, Mimumu, mo...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202719_0140
rows.name:
I should have listened
to you more, too, mo.

rows.label: qst202719_0150
rows.name: [ML:Dash ]That person taught me that, mo.

rows.label: qst202719_0160
rows.name: Hmph...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202719_0170
rows.name: Mei, families are nice, aren't they?

rows.label: qst202719_0180
rows.name: I suppose...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202719_0190
rows.name:
Everyone in this world is connected
to at least one other person.

rows.label: qst202719_0200
rows.name: It's not a bad thing to cherish them...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202719_0210
rows.name:
Just like the [System:Ruby rt=Fesseln]chained bond[/System:Ruby]
between me and my Driver.
